        <div class="workout-card">
            <div class="workout-container">
            <div class="workout-title">Chest Opens</div>
            <div class="workout-button"><img src="./assets/images/n64_b.png"></div>
            <div class="reps">4 sets of 15</div>
            <div class="workout-images">
                <img src="./assets/images/link_chest.png">
                <img src="./assets/images/bb_curl.png">
            </div>
            <div class="workout-description">
                <ul>
                <li>Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, solid like a Hylian warrior ready for battle. Position yourself directly in front of the chest, ensuring you're balanced and stable. This stance is the foundation of your heroic feat.</li>
                <li>Place your hands on the edge of the chest's lid, your palms facing upward. Your hands should be shoulder-width apart, ready to harness the power within.</li>
                <li>As you exhale, begin to lift the lid by bending your elbows, keeping them close to your torso.</li>
                <li>As the lid reaches the peak of its arc, hold it there for a moment. Feel the rush of triumph and the surge of heroic energy. This is your moment of glory, akin to holding the Master Sword aloft.</li>
                <li>With the treasure now revealed, slowly lower the lid back to its original position, maintaining control and poise.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="workout-comment">
                <p>"SEIYYIIIIIAI!‚Äù</p>
                <p>:</p>
                <p id="quote">(Link - Legend of Zelda)</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>

          <div class="workout-card">
            <div class="workout-container">
            <div class="workout-title">Wire Chokes</div>
            <div class="workout-button"><img src="./assets/images/psTri_button.png">[HOLD]</div>
            <div class="reps">3 Sets of 10</div>
            <div class="workout-images">
                <img src="./assets/images/hitman_choke.png">
                <img src="./assets/images/hammer_curl.png">
            </div>
            <div class="workout-description">
                <ul>
                <li>Identify a secure location, ideally a gym with minimal foot traffic. This will be your operational ground for the exercise.</li>
                <li>Locate target and equip fiber wire. Grip the handles firmly, ensuring they are secure.</li>
                <li>Discreetly engage biceps and strangle target (video game character), maintaining a firm grip on the wire.</li>
                <li>At the apex of the curl, contract your biceps tightly, akin to the final moment of a wire choke. Hold this position briefly to maximize muscle engagement.</li>
                <li>Slowly lower the fiber wire back to the starting position.</li>
                    <span id = "red">--important note: DO NOT ATTEMPT THIS IN REAL LIFE</span>
                     </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="workout-comment">
            <p>"We dertemine who we are by what we do"</p>
            <p>:</p>
            <p id="quote">(Agent 47 - Hitman)</p>        
